10#ifndef MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTP_VIDEO_HEADER_H_
11#define MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTP_VIDEO_HEADER_H_
12
13#include <bitset>
14#include <cstdint>
15
16#include "absl/container/inlined_vector.h"
17#include "absl/types/optional.h"
18#include "absl/types/variant.h"
19#include "api/transport/rtp/dependency_descriptor.h"
20#include "api/video/color_space.h"
21#include "api/video/video_codec_type.h"
22#include "api/video/video_content_type.h"
23#include "api/video/video_frame_type.h"
24#include "api/video/video_rotation.h"
25#include "api/video/video_timing.h"
26#include "modules/video_coding/codecs/h264/include/h264_globals.h"
27#include "modules/video_coding/codecs/h265/include/h265_globals.h"
28#include "modules/video_coding/codecs/vp8/include/vp8_globals.h"
29#include "modules/video_coding/codecs/vp9/include/vp9_globals.h"
30
31namespace webrtc {
32// Details passed in the rtp payload for legacy generic rtp packetizer.
33// TODO(bugs.webrtc.org/9772): Deprecate in favor of passing generic video
34// details in an rtp header extension.
35struct RTPVideoHeaderLegacyGeneric {
36 uint16_t picture_id;
37};
38
39using RTPVideoTypeHeader = absl::variant<absl::monostate,
40 RTPVideoHeaderVP8,
41 RTPVideoHeaderVP9,
42 RTPVideoHeaderH264,
43#ifndef DISABLE_H265
44 RTPVideoHeaderH265,
45#endif
46 RTPVideoHeaderLegacyGeneric>;
47
48struct RTPVideoHeader {
49 struct GenericDescriptorInfo {
50 GenericDescriptorInfo();
51 GenericDescriptorInfo(const GenericDescriptorInfo& other);
52 ~GenericDescriptorInfo();
53
54 int64_t frame_id = 0;
55 int spatial_index = 0;
56 int temporal_index = 0;
57 absl::InlinedVector<DecodeTargetIndication, 10> decode_target_indications;
58 absl::InlinedVector<int64_t, 5> dependencies;
59 absl::InlinedVector<int, 4> chain_diffs;
60 std::bitset<32> active_decode_targets = ~uint32_t{0};
61 };
62
63 RTPVideoHeader();
64 RTPVideoHeader(const RTPVideoHeader& other);
65
66 ~RTPVideoHeader();
67
68 absl::optional<GenericDescriptorInfo> generic;
69
70 VideoFrameType frame_type = VideoFrameType::kEmptyFrame;
71 uint16_t width = 0;
72 uint16_t height = 0;
73 VideoRotation rotation = VideoRotation::kVideoRotation_0;
74 VideoContentType content_type = VideoContentType::UNSPECIFIED;
75 bool is_first_packet_in_frame = false;
76 bool is_last_packet_in_frame = false;
77 bool is_last_frame_in_picture = true;
78 uint8_t simulcastIdx = 0;
79 VideoCodecType codec = VideoCodecType::kVideoCodecGeneric;
80
81 VideoPlayoutDelay playout_delay;
82 VideoSendTiming video_timing;
83 absl::optional<ColorSpace> color_space;
84 // This field is meant for media quality testing purpose only. When enabled it
85 // carries the webrtc::VideoFrame id field from the sender to the receiver.
86 absl::optional<uint16_t> video_frame_tracking_id;
87 RTPVideoTypeHeader video_type_header;
88};
89
90} // namespace webrtc
91
92#endif // MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTP_VIDEO_HEADER_H_
